---

<div class="discovery-section">
    <div class="discovery-header">
        <span class="discovery-label">Discover More</span>
        <h2 class="discovery-title">SYNCODEをさらに深く探索する</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="discovery-grid">
        <a href="/works/" class="discovery-card">
            <div class="card-content">
                <span class="card-category">Portfolio</span>
                <h3 class="card-title">WORKS</h3>
                <p class="card-desc">AIとの共創によって具現化されたプロジェクトの実例と成果。</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card-footer">実績を見る</div>
        </a>

        <a href="/tools/" class="discovery-card">
            <div class="card-content">
                <span class="card-category">Resources</span>
                <h3 class="card-title">TOOLS</h3>
                <p class="card-desc">日々の開発や執筆を支える、厳選されたAIツール・技術スタック。</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card-footer">ツール一覧へ</div>
        </a>
    </div>
</div>

<style>
    .discovery-section {
        margin: 100px 0 60px;
        padding-top: 60px;
        border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
        width: 100%;
    }

    .discovery-header {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 50px;
    }

    .discovery-label {
        font-size: 0.7rem;
        font-weight: 500;
        letter-spacing: 0.3em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: var(--color-text-light);
        display: block;
        margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .discovery-title {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        font-weight: 300;
        letter-spacing: 0.1em;
        margin: 0;
    }

    .discovery-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
        gap: 20px;
        max-width: 1100px;
        margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .discovery-card {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: space-between;
        padding: 40px;
        background-color: #fafafa;
        border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
        text-decoration: none;
        color: var(--color-text);
        transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.165, 0.84, 0.44, 1);
    }

    .discovery-card:hover {
        background-color: #fff;
        border-color: #333;
        transform: translateY(-4px);
        box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
    }

    .card-category {
        font-size: 0.65rem;
        letter-spacing: 0.15em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: #888;
        display: block;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .card-title {
        font-size: 1.25rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: 0.2em;
        margin: 0 0 16px 0;
    }

    .card-desc {
        font-size: 0.85rem;
        line-height: 1.8;
        color: var(--color-text-light);
        margin: 0;
    }

    .card-footer {
        margin-top: 40px;
        font-size: 0.75rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: 0.1em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
    }

    .card-footer::after {
        content: "";
        width: 20px;
        height: 1px;
        background-color: var(--color-text);
        margin-left: 12px;
        transition: width 0.3s ease;
    }

    .discovery-card:hover .card-footer::after {
        width: 40px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .discovery-grid {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }
        .discovery-card {
            padding: 30px;
        }
    }
</style>
